==English==
===Idiom===
'''to [[know]] [[like]] [[the]] [[back]] [[of]] [[one]]'s [[hand]]'''

#To be intimately familiar with something.  To know every smallest detail about something.  Frequently used in reference to a particular locale.  Usually not used when referring to another person.

